[risk_super]
param.uc_lookup_path = <string> Risk use case lookup path. It's a required parameter.
param.uc_ref_field = <string> Use case ref lookup field name. It's a required parameter.
param.dedup = <list> Dedup risk events.  It's default value is 0.
param.min_sec_since_last_riskevent = <string> Minimum seconds since last risk event.  It's default value is 1800.
